title: NYC MAGIC: SUPRA IN THE CITY
description:
The much anticipated video from the SUPRA team's trip last year to New York City with TransWorld Magazine is now available for your viewing pleasure. Starring: Chad Muska, Neen Williams, Erik Ellington, Keelan Dadd, Spencer Hamilton, Kevin Romar, Furby, Jim Greco, Stevie Williams, Matt Mumford, Boo Johnson, and Ben James.
